<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> | Utah Home Ready Check</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .agent-nav { background: var(--blue); padding: 15px 0; }
        .agent-nav .container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .agent-nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 20px; }
        .code-block { background: var(--dark); color: #a5d6ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.875rem; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="agent-nav">
        <div class="container">
            <div>
                <a href="/agent-portal/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/agent-portal/leads">My Leads</a>
                <a href="/agent-portal/settings">Settings</a>
                <a href="/agent-portal/embed"><strong>Embed Code</strong></a>
            </div>
            <a href="/agent-portal/logout">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="mb-3">Embed Code for Your Website</h1>

            <div class="card mb-3">
                <h3 class="mb-2">Your Assessment Link</h3>
                <p>Share this link directly with potential buyers:</p>
                <code style="display: block; background: var(--bg); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <%= baseUrl %>/agent/<%= agent.slug %>
                </code>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-3">
                <h3 class="mb-2">Embed as iFrame</h3>
                <p>Add this code to your website to embed the assessment:</p>
                <div class="code-block">&lt;iframe
    src="<%= baseUrl %>/agent/<%= agent.slug %>/embed"
    width="100%"
    height="700"
    frameborder="0"
    style="border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"&gt;
&lt;/iframe&gt;</div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="mb-2">Add as Button</h3>
                <p>Or add a button that links to your assessment:</p>
                <div class="code-block">&lt;a href="<%= baseUrl %>/agent/<%= agent.slug %>"
   target="_blank"
   style="display: inline-block; background: #22c55e; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;"&gt;
    Check Your Home Readiness
&lt;/a&gt;</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
